fzuzeigen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 4aBiologieunterricht. 4aDeutsch als Zweitsprache. 4aDeutschdidaktik. 4aGerman as a second language. 4aZweitspracherwerb. 4asecond language acquisition. 4ateaching German. 4ateaching biology. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2016z9783110485257oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831104520680 cprintz978311045118440uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311045423940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110454239423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110454239.jpg  a978-3-11-070100-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2016  aZDB-23-DSPb2016